Incogitancy	#452.	 unbend the mind, relax the mind, divert the mind, veg out. Adj. vacant, unintellectual, unideal, unoccupied, unthinking, inconsiderate, thoughtless, mindless, no-brain, vacuous
Inattention	#458.	 heedless, careless &c. (neglectful). inconsiderate, thoughtless. absent, abstracted, distrait
Neglect	#460.	 heedless, careless, thoughtless
Nonpreparation	#674.	 dismantled &c. v.. shiftless, improvident, unthrifty, thriftless, thoughtless, unguarded
